@baseUrl = http://localhost:1337/api/v1

### Register
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@test.com",
    "password": "123456"
}

### Login
# @name loginRequest
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@test.com",
    "password": "123456"
}

### Ruta protegida
GET http://localhost:1337/health
Authorization: Bearer {{loginRequest.response.body.token}}